Sect. 12. Second Motive taken from the Mischievous Consequents of not Heeding divine Warnings, and these,



      1. In regard of Sin, which is thereby much aggravated;


      2. Of Punishment, which such Heedlesness doth, 1. Necessitate, 2. Precipitate, 3. Aggravate. p. 35

